Note that the formats used by `LocalDate` &amp; `LocalDateRange` when parsing/generating text are standard [ISO 8601][7] formats.

## Database

You could use a database for your purpose, but that would be overkill if you read/write the data file in a single thread. If you need to manage data across threads, then use a database engine such as [H2][8]. 


